ects Peredur's suit, but later falls in love with him when he comes back as the unknown Mute Knight. The name has been strongly revived in Wales since the 1940s, borne, for example, by the actress  Angharad Rees  (  1949-2012 )."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Angharad ferch Ednyfed Fychan was born about 1185, in Clwyd, Wales, United Kingdom, her father, Ednyfed Fychan ap Cynwrig of Dules, was 37 and her mother, Nest Annest Agnes Gwenllian Verch Rhys, was 39. She married Einion Fychan ap Einion in 1245, in Wales, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 4 sons."},"et":{"about 1185–":"umbes 1185–Surnud","1165–1260":"1165–1260","1185–Female":"1185–Surnud","1193–Male":"1193–Surnud","1195–Female":"1195–Surnud","1200–1277":"1200–1277","1220–Male":"1220–Surnud","1307–Male":"1307–Surnud","1150–1246":"1150–1246","1235–Male":"1235–Surnud","1270–1370":"1270–1370","–1300":"–1300","1148–1236":"1148–1236","1220":"1220","1165":"1165","1185":"1185","1195":"1195","1370":"1370","1150":"1150","1260":"1260","1270":"1270","1193":"1193","1236":"1236","1148":"1148","1235":"1235","1246":"1246","1245":"1245","1300":"1300","1277":"1277","1200":"1200","about 1235":"umbes 1235","Abt 1270":"umbes 1270","about 1185":"umbes 1185","1307":"1307","Wales, United Kingdom":"Wales, United Kingdom","Merioneth, Glamorgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales, United Kingdom","Wales":"Wales, United Kingdom","Clwyd, Wales, United Kingdom":"Clwyd, Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1185–":"noin 1185–Kuollut","1165–1260":"1165–1260","1185–Female":"1185–Kuollut","1193–Male":"1193–Kuollut","1195–Female":"1195–Kuollut","1200–1277":"1200–1277","1220–Male":"1220–Kuollut","1307–Male":"1307–Kuollut","1150–1246":"1150–1246","1235–Male":"1235–Kuollut","1270–1370":"1270–1370","–1300":"–1300","1148–1236":"1148–1236","1220":"1220","1165":"1165","1185":"1185","1195":"1195","1370":"1370","1150":"1150","1260":"1260","1270":"1270","1193":"1193","1236":"1236","1148":"1148","1235":"1235","1246":"1246","1245":"1245","1300